{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/9e/03/2328_crt_rSibq.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/9e/03/2328_crt_rSibq.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/9e/03/2328_crt_rSibq.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/9e/03/2328_crt_rSibq.jpg"},"name":"緋村剣心","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/0d/e5/3992_seiyu_anidb.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/0d/e5/3992_seiyu_anidb.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/0d/e5/3992_seiyu_anidb.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/0d/e5/3992_seiyu_anidb.jpg"},"name":"涼風真世","short_summary":"日本の女優、声優、歌手。元宝塚歌劇団月組トップスター。\r\n\r\n宮城県石巻市出身。愛称は本名の「かなめ」で、個人事務所の名称にもなっている。身長166cm、血液型はO型。大阪薫英女子高等学校卒業。\r\n\r\n声優としてはアニメ『るろうに剣心』の緋村剣心役として知られる。","career":["seiyu","actor"],"id":3992,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":2328},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/db/60/5829_crt_vtnRW.jpg?r=1542211130","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/db/60/5829_crt_vtnRW.jpg?r=1542211130","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/db/60/5829_crt_vtnRW.jpg?r=1542211130","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/db/60/5829_crt_vtnRW.jpg?r=1542211130"},"name":"斎藤一","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/65/16/3989_seiyu_anidb.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/65/16/3989_seiyu_anidb.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/65/16/3989_seiyu_anidb.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/65/16/3989_seiyu_anidb.jpg"},"name":"鈴置洋孝","short_summary":"日本の声優、俳優、ナレーターであり、劇団プロデューサー。\r\n\r\n愛知県名古屋市出身、東京経済大学卒業。身長166 cm、体重59kg。血液型はA型。","career":["seiyu"],"id":3989,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":5829},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/8c/1f/6108_crt_evVzE.jpg?r=1541942731","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/8c/1f/6108_crt_evVzE.jpg?r=1541942731","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/8c/1f/6108_crt_evVzE.jpg?